rows.label: qst103610_msg0002
rows.name:
What are you saying, mo? You are
the master of betrayal, mo.

rows.label: qst103610_msg0003
rows.name:
It was good that you weakened
the anti- regime organization
within the Empire, Brionac, mo.

rows.label: qst103610_msg0004
rows.name:
But losing Akatsuki and the
others we had infiltrated...

rows.label: qst103610_msg0005
rows.name:
And bringing uninvited
guests was a failure, mo.
